        {
            "title": "特朗普：撤回唐纳德·科布为财政部助理总法律顾问的提名。",
            "id": 1256292,
            "description": "",
            "link": "https://www.fx168news.com/express/fastnews/1256292",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-15 03:47:02",
